" Compile TeX file into PDF using PDFLaTeX
inoremap <silent> <F5> <C-o>:w <CR><C-o> :!clear; pdflatex % <CR>;
nnoremap <silent> <F5> :w <CR> :!clear; pdflatex %;<CR>

