" Open the compiled PDF using Zathura
nnoremap <silent> <F6> :!$READER <C-R>=expand('%:r').'.pdf'<CR>& :<ESC><CR>
inoremap <silent> <F6> <C-o>:!$READER <C-R>=expand('%:r').'.pdf'<CR>& :<ESC><CR>

